flowchart TD
    A[Eval Dataset] --> B[Eval Questions]
    B --> C[Start Eval Run]
    C --> D[For each question]

    D --> E[Run project-scoped retrieval]
    E --> F[Compute retrieval hit]
    F --> G{run_generation?}

    G -->|yes| H[Run chat answer generation]
    H --> I[Compute citation coverage]
    H --> J[Compute refusal behavior]

    G -->|no| K[Skip generation metrics]

    I --> L[Store eval_result]
    J --> L
    K --> L
    F --> L

    L --> M{More questions?}
    M -->|yes| D
    M -->|no| N[Aggregate run metrics]
    N --> O[Store eval_run metrics]

    O --> P[Project metrics summary]
    Q[Retrieval logs] --> P
    R[Feedback] --> P
    S[Documents and chunks] --> P

    subgraph Isolation[Project Isolation]
        X[dataset.project_id]
        Y[question.project_id]
        Z[run.project_id]
        W[result.project_id]
    end

    C -. validate .-> X
    D -. validate .-> Y
    O -. store .-> Z
    L -. store .-> W
